==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: papoose root
<hw>papoose root</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A tall herb (<spn>Caulophyllum
thalictroides</spn>) of eastern North America and Asia having blue
berrylike fruit and a thick knotty rootstock formerly used medicinally;
the <altname>Cohosh</altname>. See also <er>Cohosh</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blue cohosh, blueberry root, papoose root,
squawroot, squaw root, Caulophyllum thalictrioides, <spn>Caulophyllum
thalictroides</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pappose</ent>⟦br⟧
